  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2032422/" class="title-link">美国：恐怖主义帝国的君主</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2032422"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mrsun/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3349925-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mrsun/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">俺老孫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-05-20"
      class="main-meta">2009-05-20 13:57:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2032422_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  　　“圣•奥古斯丁讲过一个故事，亚历山大大帝曾经问被他俘虏的一个海盗：‘你凭什么敢横行海上？’海盗反驳道：‘你凭什么敢横行世界？就因为我只有一艘小船，人们骂我是贼。但是因为你有一支强大的舰队，你被尊为君主。” 　　这个回答 “……在某种程度上准确地抓住了当...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2032422/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2032422_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2032422_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





